  ('social-worker-moex-04425', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Fiedler是領導理論中權變模式的先驅，下列何者不是Fiedler所認為的情境因素？', '["領導者的領導行為", "領導者與成員間的關係", "任務工作結構", "職位的權力"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "071fe21ab11a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ff31968f6db1", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "105", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
